## Key Design Decisions

1. **Monorepo Structure** — All 3 services (frontend, backend, ai-service) in one project directory for easy management
2. **JWT-based Auth** — Stateless authentication, tokens stored in `localStorage` with refresh mechanism
3. **Role-Based Routing** — React Router with protected routes per role
4. **Case Number Format** — `CASE-{YEAR}-{CATEGORY_CODE}-{SEQUENCE}` (e.g., `CASE-2026-CIV-000001`)
5. **WebSocket for Real-time** — Chat and notifications use WebSocket (STOMP over SockJS)
6. **File Storage** — Local filesystem with structured folders per case (swappable to S3)
7. **AI Integration** — Spring Boot proxies requests to FastAPI; fallback mock responses when AI service is down
8. **Responsive Design** — Mobile-first approach with Tailwind breakpoints
